timing_suppre...ape_characters(25.10)    timing_suppre...ape_characters(25.10)

Name
       timing_suppress_escape_characters

Syntax
       timing_suppress_escape_characters

       {true | false}

       Default: true

       Supresses the reporting of escape characters in timing object names.

       When  the  global is set to true, all the reporting and collection com-
       mands report the timing objects names (e.g., pins, ports, or instances)
       without the escape characters.

       To set this global variable, use the set_global command.

